TITLE: Configuring Hono API with Fiberplane and OpenAPI Integration
DESCRIPTION: Sets up a Hono API instance with Fiberplane integration and OpenAPI specification generation. Creates an endpoint at /openapi.json to serve the API specification and mounts the Fiberplane middleware at /fp/* path.
