TITLE: Creating Custom Zod Validator Middleware with Error Handling
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a custom validation middleware that wraps @hono/zod-validator with standardized error handling. This approach ensures consistent error responses across all routes while maintaining type safety through TypeScript generics.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fiberplane/fiberplane/blob/main/www/src/content/blog/2025-02-04-hono-validation-middleware.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_2

