LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
// Shared Reference (&)
& variable     // "You can look, but you can't touch. And when you're done, I want it back."

// Mutable Reference (&mut)
&mut variable  // "You can look and touch  but when you're done, I still want it back."

// Owned Value
variable       // "Here you can have it. You can do anything you want with it."

// Reference Counted (Rc/Arc)
Rc::new(value) // "Everyone can look at it, and we'll clean up when everyone is done."
```

